    <item>
      <title>选举机构发现 AMLO 盟友未获得参议院绝对多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/electoral-body-finds-amlo-allies-short-of-senate-supermajority</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据国家选举机构周五做出的最终决定，当 9 月新立法会议开幕时，总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔的“更多党”及其盟友将在墨西哥众议院占据绝对多数，但在参议院中仅比三分之二多数少两个席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/electoral-body-finds-amlo-allies-short-of-senate-supermajority</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 00:00:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据美联社报道，德国节日期间发生持刀袭击事件，造成人员死亡和受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-23/urgent-an-attack-at-a-festival-in-a-german-city-leaves-dead-and-wounded-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国索林根（美联社）——当局称，周五晚间，在德国西部城市索林根的一个节日活动中，一名持刀袭击者杀死了 3 人，至少 5 人受重伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-23/urgent-an-attack-at-a-festival-in-a-german-city-leaves-dead-and-wounded-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 21:09:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称经济增长将为减税支付数万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/trump-says-growth-will-pay-for-tax-cuts-said-to-cost-trillions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普在 11 月大选访问一个关键摇摆州时强调了他的税收议程，他表示，延长即将到期的减税政策的计划将通过刺激经济增长获得回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/trump-says-growth-will-pay-for-tax-cuts-said-to-cost-trillions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 20:51:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼迪支持特朗普，暂停非总统竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/kennedy-to-endorse-trump-for-president-ending-outsider-2024-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小罗伯特·F·肯尼迪表示，他将暂停总统竞选，转而支持共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普，从而结束了旨在为选民提供主要政党候选人之外的替代选择的失败竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/kennedy-to-endorse-trump-for-president-ending-outsider-2024-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 18:27:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗竞争对手因上传委内瑞拉投票记录被传唤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/maduro-rival-summoned-over-uploaded-venezuelan-voting-records</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉最高检察官传唤反对派领导人埃德蒙多·冈萨雷斯 (Edmundo González)，指控他上传了投票记录，这些记录似乎显示他在上个月的总统选举中以压倒性优势获胜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/maduro-rival-summoned-over-uploaded-venezuelan-voting-records</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 17:38:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本领导人候选人及其关键政策立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/who-could-replace-kishida-candidates-who-could-be-japan-s-new-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄于 8 月 14 日表示，他不会参加下个月举行的执政党自民党总裁选举，此后日本将迎来新领导人。由于自民党在议会中占据主导地位，自民党总裁几乎肯定会成为首相。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/who-could-replace-kishida-candidates-who-could-be-japan-s-new-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 02:41:28 GMT</pubDate>
